and `30min` intervals for US equities.\\nOpen, high, low, close values are supplied without volume.\"}},{\"name\":\"eod\",\"type\":\"boolean\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"If true, then return data for closed day\"}},{\"name\":\"rolling_period\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Number of hours for calculate rolling change at period. By default set to 24, it can be in range [1, 168].\"}},{\"name\":\"dp\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Specifies the number of decimal places for floating values\\nShould be in range [0,11] inclusive\"}},{\"name\":\"timezone\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Timezone at which output datetime will be displayed. Supports:\\n<ul>\\n<li>1. <code>Exchange</code> for local exchange time</li>\\n<li>2. <code>UTC</code> for datetime at universal UTC standard</li>\\n<li>3. Timezone name according to the IANA Time Zone Database. E.g. <code>America/New_York</code>, <code>Asia/Singapore</code>. Full list of timezones can be found <a href=\\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones\\\" target=\\\"blank\\\">here</a>.</li>\\n</ul>\\n<i>Take note that the IANA Timezone name is case-sensitive</i>\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"symbol\":\"AAPL\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Financial APIs providing real-time, historical, and EOD data for stocks, forex, cryptocurrency, ETFs, commodities, and fundamental market data. If the parameters of the tool include symbol, figi, isin, and cusip, one of these four parameters must be selected as a required parameter.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":0.596,\"success_rate\":1.0}}],\"search_id\":\"491acef0-ea53-4522-8740-46c92e41de59\",\"elapsed_time_ms\":386.13}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772594006195}}
{"type":"message","id":"84deab16","parentId":"15e3c76d","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:13:36.536Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The ths_ifind tool keeps failing. It seems like there's a bug in how QVeris handles the tool execution. The error message \"缺少必需的查询参数: 'codes'\" is odd because we're clearly passing the codes parameter. \n\nLet me try to see if there's another way to get Chinese stock data. Let me search for a different approach.","thinkingSignature":"01ada17b3025f59811099a7f7da8bd5fe2f6947998ffa6b8c050a2ed98b88af7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1k3sq24pwadb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST https://qveris.ai/api/v1/search \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk-qDHmOX32qh6xAKJbeilhC6pIzrLNfUJyiMTaowGr2RA\" \\\n  -d '{\"query\": \"A股 实时行情 API\", \"limit\": 5}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":15300,"output":190,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":29474,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772594006204}}
{"type":"message","id":"50904ece","parentId":"84deab16","timestamp":"2026-03-04T03:13:42.596Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1k3sq24pwadb_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\":\"A股 实时行情 API\",\"total\":5,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\"name\":\"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\"description\":\"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"codes\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":\"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"},{\"name\":\"indicators\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":\"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"codes\":\"300033.SZ,600030.SH\"}},\"provider_description\":\"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1667.64,\"success_rate\":0.887}},{\"tool_id\":\"alphavantage.apo.retrieve.v1.467a92c0\",\"name\":\"APO (Absolute Price Oscillator)\",\"description\":\"This API returns the absolute price oscillator (APO) values. See also: mathematical reference.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"function\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The technical indicator of your choice. In this case, function=APO\"},\"enum\":[\"APO\"]},{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The name of the ticker of your choice. For example: symbol=IBM\"}},{\"name\":\"interval\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Time interval between two consecutive data points in the time series. The following values are supported: 1min, 5min, 15min, 30min, 60min, daily, weekly, monthly\"},\"enum\":[\"1min\",\"5min\",\"15min\",\"30min\",\"60min\",\"daily\",\"weekly\",\"monthly\"]},{\"name\":\"series_type\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"The desired price type in the time series. Four types are supported: close, open, high, low\"},\"enum\":[\"close\",\"open\",\"high\",\"low\"]},{\"name\":\"month\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, this parameter is not set and the technical indicator values will be calculated based on the default length of the underlying intraday, daily, weekly, or monthly time series data. You can use the month parameter (in YYYY-MM format) to return technical indicators for a specific month in history. For example, month=2009-01.\"}},{\"name\":\"fastperiod\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Positive integers are accepted. By default, fastperiod=12.\"}},{\"name\":\"slowperiod\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Positive integers are accepted. By default, slowperiod=26.\"}},{\"name\":\"matype\",\"type\":\"integer\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Moving average type. By default, matype=0. Integers 0 - 8 are accepted with the following mappings. 0 = Simple Moving Average (SMA), 1 = Exponential Moving Average (EMA), 2 = Weighted Moving Average (WMA), 3 = Double Exponential Moving Average (DEMA), 4 = Triple Exponential Moving Average (TEMA), 5 = Triangular Moving Average (TRIMA), 6 = T3 Moving Average, 7 = Kaufman Adaptive Moving Average (KAMA), 8 = MESA Adaptive Moving Average (MAMA).\"},\"enum\":[\"0\",\"1\",\"2\",\"3\",\"4\",\"5\",\"6\",\"7\",\"8\"]},{\"name\":\"datatype\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"By default, datatype=json. Strings json and csv are accepted with the following specifications: json returns the daily time series in JSON format; csv returns the time series as a CSV (comma separated value) file.\"},\"enum\":[\"json\",\"csv\"]}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"symbol\":\"IBM\",\"function\":\"APO\",\"interval\":\"daily\",\"series_type\":\"close\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Alpha Vantage provides realtime and historical financial market data through a set of powerful and developer-friendly data APIs and spreadsheets. From traditional asset classes (e.g., stocks, ETFs, mutual funds) to economic indicators, from foreign exchange rates to commodities, from fundamental data to technical indicators, Alpha Vantage is your one-stop-shop for enterprise-grade global market data delivered through cloud-based APIs, MCP servers, spreadsheets, and more.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":812.96,\"success_rate\":0.562}},{\"tool_id\":\"ths_ifind.quotation.v1\",\"name\":\"iFinD 同花顺行情 (历史+实时) (THS Quotation)\",\"description\":\"Query historical and real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, supporting price, trading volume, turnover ratio, and other indicators for various financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"codes\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":\"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"},{\"name\":\"indicators\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":\"Indicator list, comma-separated. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom list. Default is 'all'. Applies to both history and real-time calls.\"},{\"name\":\"startdate\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":\"Start date, formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'\"},{\"name\":\"enddate\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":\"End date, formats: 'YYYY-MM-DD', 'YYYY/MM/DD', 'YYYYMMDD'\"},{\"name\":\"interval\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":\"Time period: 'D' (daily), 'W' (weekly), 'M' (monthly), 'Q' (quarterly), 'S' (semi-annual), 'Y' (yearly), default 'D'\"},{\"name\":\"cps\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":\"Adjustment method: '1' (no adjustment), '2' (forward), '3' (backward), '6' (forward cash dividend), '7' (backward cash dividend), default '1'\"},{\"name\":\"fill\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":\"Non-trading day handling: 'Previous' (use previous data), 'Blank' (empty), default 'Previous'\"}],\"provider_description\":\"同花顺 (THS) iFinD data provider, offering financial data for Chinese and international markets including stocks, securities, funds, bonds, futures, etc. Supports company announcements, intelligent stock screening, industry analysis, market trend prediction, and more, helping users conduct comprehensive financial data analysis and investment decisions.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":2750.14,\"success_rate\":0.9}},{\"tool_id\":\"eodhd.live_prices.retrieve.v1.178541d4\",\"name\":\"Live (Delayed) Stock Prices\",\"description\":\"Retrieve live or delayed stock prices and macroeconomic data.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"ticker\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Ticker symbol with exchange suffix (e.g., AAPL.US).\"}},{\"name\":\"s\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Optional filter parameter.\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"ticker\":\"AAPL.US\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Access historical end-of-day stock prices, intraday data, US stock options, and real-time prices with free and advanced plans. EODHD provides financial data for 150,000+ tickers, including stocks, ETFs, funds, and currencies worldwide.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1207.16,\"success_rate\":0.946}},{\"tool_id\":\"finnhub_io_api.stock.quote\",\"name\":\"Quote\",\"description\":\"Get real-time quote data for US stocks.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":\"Stock symbol\"}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"symbol\":\"AAPL\"}},\"provider_description\":\"Finnhub - Free APIs for realtime stock, forex, and cryptocurrency. Company fundamentals, Economic data, and Alternative data.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":853.46,\"success_rate\":0.951}}],\"search_id\":\"2408a856-cf41-4009-b48a-eb92d6810c80\",\"elapsed_time_ms\":321.57}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6055,"aggregated":"{\"query\":\"A股 实时行情 API\",\"total\":5,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"ths_ifind.real_time_quotation.v1\",\"name\":\"iFinD 同花顺实时行情 (THS Real-time Quotation)\",\"description\":\"Query real-time quotation data for securities in the 同花顺 (THS) iFinD database, providing real-time market data for financial products including stocks, funds, bonds, and futures, such as real-time prices, trading volumes, price changes, bid/ask quotes, etc. Supports querying various real-time indicators including latest price, price change, trading volume, turnover ratio, market value, and five-level bid/ask quotes.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"codes\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":\"Security codes, multiple codes separated by commas (max 50), e.g., '300033.SZ,600030.SH'\"},{\"name\":\"indicators\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":false,\"description\":\"Indicator list, multiple indicators separated by commas. Options: 'common' (common indicators), 'all' (all indicators), or custom indicator list. Default is 'all'\"}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"codes\":\"300033.SZ,600030.SH